LBumper:
Loop, %MouseWheelNumber% {
	Send {WheelUp}
	Sleep, %MouseWheelDelay% ; I not understand why SetKeyDelay not working for this Loop :(
}
return


RBumper:
Loop, %MouseWheelNumber% {
	Send {WheelDown}
	Sleep, %MouseWheelDelay% ; Without this Sleep, scroll to N lines will not work
}
return


